txt.en: Lake-town Smugglers and knife-throwers can be found inside the Smugglers' hideout in Lake-town.\n\nYou should defeat Lake-town Smugglers and knife-throwers.
Dagrun can be found in the Council of Wares Headquarters.\n\nYou should talk to Dagrun.
The Lake-town Smugglers have been disrupting Dale for far too long and need to be pushed out. Defeat any smugglers found within their hideout.
